# This file ensures the logs/ directory exists for application logging
#
# LifeBuddy uses Python's logging library with both console and file output.
# Logs are automatically rotated (10MB max, 5 backups) to prevent disk bloat.
#
# Log files that will appear here (excluded by .gitignore):
# - app.log (General application logs - rotating)
# - health_processing.log (Apple Health data processing)
# - fastapi.log (FastAPI backend logs)
# - streamlit.log (Streamlit frontend logs)
# - ollama.log (Ollama connection and model logs)
# - agents.log (AI agent interactions)
#
# Console output: INFO level and above with emojis
# File output: DEBUG level and above with full timestamps 